@startuml Create and Assign Chore Sequence

actor Parent
participant UI
participant API
participant ChoreService
participant EventBus
participant NotificationService

Parent -> UI: Create new chore
UI -> UI: Display chore form
Parent -> UI: Enter chore details
UI -> API: POST /api/chores
API -> ChoreService: CreateChore(command)
ChoreService -> ChoreService: Calculate point value
ChoreService -> EventBus: Raise ChoreCreated
ChoreService --> API: ChoreId
API --> UI: 201 Created
UI --> Parent: Success + prompt to assign

Parent -> UI: Assign chore to child
UI -> API: POST /api/chores/{id}/assign
API -> ChoreService: AssignChore(command)
ChoreService -> EventBus: Raise ChoreAssigned
ChoreService --> API: AssignmentId
API --> UI: 201 Created

EventBus -> NotificationService: ChoreAssigned event
NotificationService -> NotificationService: Send notification to child
NotificationService --> EventBus: Notification sent

UI --> Parent: Assignment confirmed

@enduml
